<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Farm Fresh - Blog</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css" />
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      color: #333;
    }
    header {
      background-color: #4CAF50;
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
    }
    nav {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 2rem;
      background: #388E3C;
      padding: 0.5rem 0;
    }
    nav a {
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .blog-container {
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 2rem auto;
      padding: 0 1rem;
    }
    .blog-post {
      background: white;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .blog-post img {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
    }
    .blog-content {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
    .blog-content h2 {
      margin-top: 0;
      color: #2e7d32;
    }
    .blog-content p {
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 1rem;
      background-color: #4CAF50;
      color: white;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <h1>AgroLink</h1>
    <p>Healthy Living Starts with Farmers</p>
  </header>

  <nav>
    <a href="/home">Home</a>
    <a href="/shop">Shop</a>
    <a href="/blog">Blog</a>
    <a href="#">Contact</a>
  </nav>

  <main class="blog-container">
    <div class="blog-post">
      
      <div class="blog-content">
        
        <img src="/img/online order.png" alt="Farmers at market">
        <h2>Why Buying Direct from Farmers Matters</h2>
        <p>Discover the benefits of supporting local agriculture and how it boosts your community, health, and environment.</p>
        <a href="#">Read More →</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="blog-post">
      <img src="/img/organic.png" alt="Organic farm">
      <div class="blog-content">
        <h2>5 Tips for Starting Your Own Organic Farm</h2>
        <p>From soil health to sustainable techniques, explore practical advice for aspiring organic farmers.</p>
        <a href="#">Read More →</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="blog-post">
      <img src="/img/hapus.png" alt="Seasonal produce">
      <div class="blog-content">
        <h2>Eating with the Seasons</h2>
        <p>Learn about seasonal produce and how aligning your meals with nature can be both delicious and economical.</p>
        <a href="#">Read More →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2025 AgroLink. Grown with love.</p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
